/**********************************************************************
==================== SESSION BASED AUTHENTICATION ====================

1) User login button click karta hai
   → Email aur password server ko bhejta hai.

2) Server database me check karta hai
   → Password match hua? ✔️

3) Server ek SESSION create karta hai.
   Example server side me:
   {
     sessionId: "abc123",
     userId: "vivek01"
   }

   Ye data server ke RAM / Redis / session store me save hota hai.

4) Server browser ko ek COOKIE bhejta hai.
   Cookie me sirf sessionId hota hai:

   sessionId = abc123

   Cookie browser me store hoti hai.

------------------ Protected Route Access ------------------

5) Jab user koi protected page open karta hai:
   → Browser automatically cookie attach karta hai.

   sessionId = abc123

6) Server cookie se sessionId leta hai
   → Apne session storage me check karta hai.
   → Agar session mil gaya ✔️
   → User authenticated.

FINAL:
Session me real data server me hota hai.
Browser me sirf sessionId hota hai.
Server ko user ko yaad rakhna padta hai.
**********************************************************************/

/**********************************************************************
======================= JWT BASED AUTHENTICATION ======================

1) User login button click karta hai
   → Email aur password server ko bhejta hai.

2) Server database me check karta hai
   → Password match hua? ✔️

3) Server ek JWT TOKEN generate karta hai.
   Token ke andar hi data hota hai:

   {
     userId: "vivek01",
     exp: "7 days"
   }

4) Server token browser ko bhejta hai.
   Token store ho sakta hai:
   → HttpOnly cookie me
   → Ya localStorage me

------------------ Protected Route Access ------------------

5) Jab user protected page open karta hai:
   → Browser token server ko bhejta hai
     (cookie ya Authorization header me)

6) Server JWT ko verify karta hai secret key se.
   → Agar valid hai ✔️
   → User authenticated.

FINAL:
JWT me server ko kuch store nahi karna padta.
Token ke andar hi data hota hai.
Server sirf verify karta hai.
Server ko user ko yaad nahi rakhna padta.
**********************************************************************/

